g.text: More options than standard canvas tools
Image support with vector graphic conversion
Support for diverse user interfaces (UI customization, dark and white mode)
Shape library for storing and reusing assets
Active Discord community for real-time discussions and support.
Twitter for updates, tips, and community highlights.
LinkedIn for professional networking and updates on Excalidraw's development and use cases.
Acknowledges an initial learning curve with compensatory depth of functionality
Deploy Excalidraw as a standalone website for enhanced accessibility and user reach
💾 Open format - export drawings as an .excalidraw json file.
⚒️ Wide range of tools - rectangle, circle, diamond, arrow, line, free-draw, eraser...
- DO BETTER WITH MORE OPTIONS THAN CANVAS
- MORE TIME TO LEARN INITIAL CURVE
- RECTANGLES / CIRCLES / DIAMANDS / LINE / ARROW / FREE-DRAW / ERASER / ETC
QUICK WAY TO EXTRACT PIC FROM WEB
- INFINITE CANVAS SPACE FOR FLEXIBILITY & CREATIVITY
- IMAGE SUPPORT WITH VECTOR GRAPHIC CONVERSION
- SUPPORT FOR DIVERSE USER INTERFACE (UI CUSTOMIZATION)
- SHAPE LIBRARY FOR STORING AND REUSING ASSETS
- ACKOWNLEDGES AN INITIAL LEARNING CURCE WITH COMPENSATORY DEPTH OF FUNCTIONALITY
- DEPLOY EXCALIDRAW AS A STANDALONE WEBSITE FOR ENHANCE ACCESSIBILITY AND USER REACH
- ACTIVE DISCORD COMMUNITY FOR REAL-TIME DISCUSSIONS AND SUPPORT
- TWITTER FOR UPDATES, TIPS, COMMUNITY HIGHLIGHTS
